Welcome to Web Lookup/Verification

  • The system works best if you ONLY fill in 1-2 fields instead of all of them.
  • If you fill in all the fields you narrow the search down to a point the system may not be able to find your file.
  • If you have partial information or are unsure of spelling use a wild card search by placing an asterisk following the data you are sure about. (Example not sure if the spelling is Alan or Allen, enter Al*).
  • Please use Firefox version 84 or newer or Chrome version 5.2.4 or newer.
